query:
SELECT
                factory_deps.bytecode,
                transactions.data AS "data?",
                transactions.contract_address AS "contract_address?"
            FROM
                (
                    SELECT
                        miniblock_number, tx_hash, topic2
                    FROM
                        events
                    WHERE
                        address = $1 AND
                        topic1 = $2 AND
                        topic4 = $3
                    LIMIT
                        1
                ) deploy_event
                JOIN factory_deps ON factory_deps.bytecode_hash = deploy_event.topic2
                LEFT JOIN transactions ON transactions.hash = deploy_event.tx_hash
            WHERE
                deploy_event.miniblock_number <= (SELECT MAX(number) FROM miniblocks)
